Class IntKMeans.Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.ml.clustering.IntCentroidsResult
      • org.openimaj.ml.clustering.kmeans.IntKMeans.Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Readable, ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteable, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary, IntNearestNeighboursProvider, CentroidsProvider<int[]>, Clusters, SpatialClusters<int[]>
    Enclosing class:
    IntKMeans

    public static class IntKMeans.Result
extends IntCentroidsResult
implements IntNearestNeighboursProvider
    Result object for IntKMeans, extending IntCentroidsResult and IntNearestNeighboursProvider, as well as giving access to state information from the operation of the K-Means algorithm (i.e. number of iterations, and convergence state).
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
